<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Further_reading">Further reading</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Science_of_science_policy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Further reading"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r1054258005">.mw-parser-output .refbegin{font-size:90%;margin-bottom:0.5em}.mw-parser-output .refbegin-hanging-indents>ul{margin-left:0}.mw-parser-output .refbegin-hanging-indents>ul>li{margin-left:0;padding-left:3.2em;text-indent:-3.2em}.mw-parser-output .refbegin-hanging-indents ul,.mw-parser-output .refbegin-hanging-indents ul li{list-style:none}@media(max-width:720px){.mw-parser-output .refbegin-hanging-indents>ul>li{padding-left:1.6em;text-indent:-1.6em}}.mw-parser-output .refbegin-columns{margin-top:0.3em}.mw-parser-output .refbegin-columns ul{margin-top:0}.mw-parser-output .refbegin-columns li{page-break-inside:avoid;break-inside:avoid-column}</style><div class="refbegin" style="">
<ul><li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFFealingLaneMarburger_IIIShipp2011" class="citation book cs1">Fealing, Kaye Husbands; Lane, Julia; Marburger III, John H.; Shipp, Stephanie S., eds. (2011). <i>The science of science policy&#160;: a handbook</i> (2nd&#160;ed.). Stanford, California: Stanford Business Books. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0804770781" title="Special:BookSources/978-0804770781"><bdi>978-0804770781</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+science+of+science+policy+%3A+a+handbook&amp;rft.place=Stanford%2C+California&amp;rft.edition=2nd&amp;rft.pub=Stanford+Business+Books&amp;rft.date=2011&amp;rft.isbn=978-0804770781&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AScience+of+science+policy" class="Z3988"></span></li></ul>
